== 制作 ==
导演{{link-en|乔纳森·格雷泽|Jonathan Glazer}}决定完成处女作《{{link-en|性感野兽|Sexy Beast}}》（2000年）后，改编[[米歇尔·法柏|米歇尔·法柏]]的小说《{{link-en|皮囊之下 (小说)|Under the Skin (novel)|皮囊之下}}》（2000年），后来又因其第二部电影《{{link-en|重生 (2004年电影)|Birth (film)|重生}}》（2004年）而搁置。他和联合编剧沃尔特·坎贝尔起初创作的剧本，讲的是两个外星人伪装成农民，由[[布拉德·皮特|布拉德·皮特]]饰演丈夫，但创作进展缓慢。格雷泽最终决定把电影拍成以一名外星人代表的视觉看待人类世界，且只着重于女性角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/mar/06/under-the-skin-director-jonathan-glazer-scarlett-johansson|title=Under the Skin: why did this chilling masterpiece take a decade?|last1=Leigh|first1=Danna|date=6 March 2014|website=The Guardian|accessdate=29 April 2014|archive-date=2014-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604192026/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/mar/06/under-the-skin-director-jonathan-glazer-scarlett-johansson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

大多数角色不会由演员扮演，约翰逊勾搭男人的许多场景，都是跟街上的男子进行不按剧本的谈话，由隐藏摄像机拍摄。格雷泽表示，“谈话展现了他们的忍耐度，如果他们同意参演这部电影，一旦他们明白我们在干什么的话<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26559813 |title=Scarlett Johansson on playing 'unscripted' scavenging alien |last1=Jones |first1=Emma |date=16 March 2014 |website=BBC News |publisher=BBC |accessdate=17 March 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316214649/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26559813 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”摩托车公路赛车冠军杰里米·麦克威廉斯饰演摩托车手，是出于要恶劣的天气条件下，在苏格兰高地高速行驶的“世界级”车手的需要。伐木工是片中一处专为影片打造的场景的主人<ref name="film4">{{cite web|url=http://www.film4.com/special-features/interviews/under-the-skin-casting|title=Under The Skin: Casting|website=Film 4|accessdate=28 June 2014|archive-date=2015-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316143247/http://www.film4.com/special-features/interviews/under-the-skin-casting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至于患上{{link-en|神经纤维瘤|Neurofibromatosis}}病的男子，格雷泽不愿使用修复术。选角时制作团队联络了支持人体面部抽搐的慈善团体“变脸”。角色落在亚当·皮尔森的头上，他曾参与电视节目制作，还就剧本中斯嘉丽的角色如何吸引他的角色给出建议<ref name="film4" />。

== 发行与评价 ==
影片于2013年8月29日在{{link-en|特柳赖德电影节|Telluride Film Festival}}首映，并在[[第70届威尼斯国际电影节|第70届威尼斯国际电影节]]和[[2013年多伦多国际影展|2013年多伦多国际影展]]首映<ref>{{cite news | url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/toronto-international-film-festival-lineup-1200566779/ | title=Toronto Intl. Film Festival Unveils First Batch of Films | work=Variety | publisher=Reed Business Information | date=23 July 2013 | accessdate=16 August 2013 | last=Punter | first=Jessie | archive-date=2017-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620122117/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/toronto-international-film-festival-lineup-1200566779/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/undertheskin | title=Under the Skin | publisher=[[多伦多国际电影节|多伦多国际电影节]] | accessdate=16 August 2013 | archive-date=2013-08-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816022137/http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/undertheskin | dead-url=no }}</ref>，2014年3月14日英国首映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a531629/scarlett-johanssons-under-the-skin-announces-uk-release-date.html |title=Scarlett Johansson's 'Under the Skin' announces UK release date – Movies News |publisher=Digital Spy |date= |accessdate=14 April 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211052853/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a531629/scarlett-johanssons-under-the-skin-announces-uk-release-date.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，4月4日登录美国<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2014/01/under-the-skin-release-date |title="Under the Skin" Scarlett Johansson Alien Movie Release Date |publisher=Complex |date=7 January 2014 |accessdate=14 April 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211055230/http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2014/01/under-the-skin-release-date |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
影片在英国以23.9万英镑的票房开画<ref>{{cite web |last=Gant |first=Charles |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/mar/19/need-for-speed-under-the-skin-uk-box-office |title=Need for Speed in pole position at UK box office but Under the Skin infectious | Film |publisher=theguardian.com |date=19 March 2014 |accessdate=14 April 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112182034/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/mar/19/need-for-speed-under-the-skin-uk-box-office |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美国，影片在四间影院上映共赚到14万美元，是影院平均票房最高的电影，超过同样由斯嘉丽主演的《[[美國隊長2：酷寒戰士|美國隊長2：酷寒戰士]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?view=&yr=2014&wknd=14&p=.htm |title=Weekend Box Office Results for April 4–6, 2014 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date= |accessdate=14 April 2014 |archive-date=2015-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403060647/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?view=&yr=2014&wknd=14&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本片在国内共赚到2614251英镑<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=undertheskin2014.htm |title=Under the Skin (2014) |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=29 December 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112180905/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=undertheskin2014.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，未能列入美国最卖座的电影列表<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/the-30-highest-grossing-indies-of-2014-a-running-list |title=The 30 Highest Grossing Indies of 2014 (A Running List) |publisher=Indiewire |date= |accessdate=2014-12-29}}</ref>，1330万美元的预算未能赚回。

=== 专业评价 ===
影片普遍获得正面评价，被众多影评人评为2014年最佳影片之一。评论集合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]基于184条评论，给予本片86%的“新鲜度”，平均得分7.9/10。该网站的共识表示：“影片的消息可能有点难以证明，但吸引人的画面和斯嘉丽·约翰逊的迷人演绎，赋予影片令人难忘的视觉体验<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/under_the_skin_2013/|title=Under the Skin (2013)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=18 December 2014|archive-date=2014-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404153404/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/under_the_skin_2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基于42条评论，给予本片78分（100分），表示“一般好评<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/under-the-skin |title=Under the Skin |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=20 April 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207072604/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/under-the-skin |dead-url=no }}</ref>”，还把本片列入2014年最佳电影榜单第四位，根据其在评论家的十佳榜单中的表现<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critic-top-10-lists-best-movies-of-2014|title = Film Critic Top 10 Lists - Best Movies of 2014|date = 6 December 2014|accessdate = 8 January 2015|website = Metacritic|publisher = |last = Dietz|first = Jason|archive-date = 2019-07-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190710180015/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critic-top-10-lists-best-movies-of-2014|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。

